review_blob: Lots of flavor, too much to describe.  Comes in a wine bottle with a cork, and dont let the unfiltered look of the beer fool you.  Great with steak and the best out of the chimay line, one bottle will make you feel pretty good.
One of the best Belgian beers i have ever tasted. Honestly think it taste better from a bottle than the tap.  An orange is a must.  One of the best beers you can buy from your local grocer.

At first does not look very appealing but after the first taste it is quite pleasing.  Very light taste resembling a belgian pills but weaker.  Goes down real smooth. Great beer to have when relaxing with a cigar when you dont want something too strong.  Wush it was sold in more areas, only know one place where i can get it.
Tastes a lot creamier and fuller out of a tap.  Out of all the beers that you can get anywhere this would be my favorite.

beer_brewer_name: Magic Hat Brewing Company (North American Breweries)
review_blob: Since I live in Florida i have not been able to try many Magic Hat beers but when vactioning in Virginia i had the oppurtunity to try this one.  This tops my list of fruit tasting beers with the hint of apricot.  Great thirst quencher and perfect for after dinner.  I just wish i could get my hands on some since i only got to try it once!!  Is there anyone who has access to this willing to do a trade???

I really havent had too many beers but for what i have tried this is my favorite.  The taste is perfectly round and not too harsh on any extreme.  The hint of lemon is a great addition as well.  One of the most thirst quenching beers i have ever tasted.
Great overall taste.  Very crisp and goes down smooth with a hint of smoked taste.  Overall one of my favorie beers!
